These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, skateboarding
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, snake
The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, nurse
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard
1. the person driving the scooter is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8
2. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the freelancer##5
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Sport      | skateboarding     | biathlon      |
| Pet          | snake | goldfish    |
| Job         | nurse   | freelancer |
| Transport   | scooter  | skateboard      |

