.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, blood-red
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, lacrosse
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, grapes
House: palace, colonial
1. the person who likes blood-red is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the person eating blueberry##5
3. the person eating grapes is not to the right of the person eating blueberry##8
4. the palace house is not the person who's sport is lacrosse##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Color    | apricot        | blood-red    |
| Sport       | rugby         | lacrosse |
| Food         | grapes | blueberry   |
| House   | palace               | colonial  |

