2. the person driving the trike is not to the right of the librarian##8
3. the victorian house is somewhere to the left of the person playing whist##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Game   | monopoly       | whist |
| House   | victorian       | cottage    |
| Transport   | scooter | trike |
| Job           | engineer        | librarian   |

