City: prague, colone
2 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, metal
1. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to colone##5
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the left of the fan of metal##8
3. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Sport         | soccer | ice-hockey  |
| City           | colone  | prague |
| Game   | scrabble | backgammon   |
| Music-Genre     | metal   | house |

