The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, house
1. the fan of house is on the far left##1
2. the person playing billiard is not to the right of the person who likes blood-red##8
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes white##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Flower   | orchid | dahlia |
